1. Do we want to make this a comparative or IR paper? Focusing on DRC seems to make it a CP paper.

2. The outbreak of civil conflict is probabaly a random case, and we need to have more controls. Especially consider controls that have been studied in the literature.

3. We need a baseline of conflict likelihood, and then examine the effect of media effect.

4. Consider the tif-for-tat dynamics between warring parties. Also there might be an influence of foreign support.
